<h5 id="subject_1126433">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;topic=126968.msg1126433#msg1126433" rel="nofollow">Re: 【Advanced Class Guide】召唤师变体：魂域召唤师（Spirit Summoner）</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1126433'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1126433'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #9 于:</strong> 2021-07-28, 周三 14:17:59 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1126433_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1126433">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; pathfinder society的博客说：The unchained summoner qualifies for all existing summoner archetypes, save those that modify the <strong>eidolon&#039;s type or base form</strong>. <a href="https://paizo.com/community/blog/v5748dyo5lheb?Society-Unchained" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">原贴地址</a><br><br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Spirit Summoner要求幻灵的形态适合魂域，这应该是限制了幻灵的类型，所以我觉得它不能应用于unchained召唤师。<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;另外，PFS Additional Resources也明确了该资源不可用于PFS。<br><br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 不过我以上依据的都是PFS规则。仅就PF规则而言，unchained只说了，除武僧外，只要有合适的特性可被替换，则以前变体都可用。按照这个说法，在PFS规则之外该变体确实是可用于unchained召唤师的。</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="moderatorbar">
